     D True            C                   *On
     D False           C                   *Off
 
      **  Fields used to check that sufficient lines remain for the
      **  printer file record format.
     D Difln1          S              2  0
     D Rqdln1          S              2  0
 
      **  Work Field used to produce only one dump.
     D W_RunBefore     S              1A
 
      **  Work Field used to open P1 printer file only once.
     D W_OpenP1        S              1A
 
